---
title: Speakers on Christianity and Transhumanism
description: Faith, Technology, and the Future. Is your church ready?
---

<div class="container">
<h1>Speakers</h1>

<p>Interested in exploring the relationship between Christianity, technology, and the future? Members of the association are available to lead classes, congregations,&nbsp;meetup groups, colleges, youth events, and other gatherings. We can conduct lively group discussions, or present stimulating ideas to serious audiences of lay people and academics.&nbsp;</p>
<p>There are lots of possibilities, and we can work with you.&nbsp;<a href="mailto:christiantranshumanism@gmail.com">Contact us</a> to discuss details!&nbsp;</p>
<hr />

    <% @speakers.each do |director| %>
      <br />
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <% if director[:url] %>
            <a href="<%= director[:url] %>">
          <% end %>
          <%= cl_image_tag(director[:photo], width: 200, height: 200, crop: :fill, gravity: 'face') %>
          <% if director[:url] %>
            </a>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h4><%= director[:name].html_safe %></h4>
          <p><%= director[:bio].html_safe %></p>
          <% if director[:url] %>
            <%= link_to "Read more &gt".html_safe, director[:url] %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>